name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Pride of the Lakes Chrome Extension

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Show local businesses in search engines. Invest in Douglas County, MN by Doing Business Locally.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Keep local stores in mind while you are searching. All you need to do is install this extension and start Googling. 

You'll see recommendations from the Pride of the Lakes website based on your search keywords. It is an easy way to support our community and keep dollars local.

FYI we are not collecting or selling any of your data.
